data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath in a very nice neighborhood.Spacious and Neat 3-Bed, 2 Bath Home with NEW Vinyl Fenced yard & Bright Florida   Grand double-door entry flows into two Living spaces. Step-down Living Room with Stone-Front wood-burning fireplace. Separate Family room. . Neutral colors throughout the house. Tile & Laminate flooring in baths & main living areas. Vaulted & Beamed ceilings in LR, FR, & MBR. Large Master Bath Has just been remolded with grantee, new faucet and much more. Multiple attic access points, including Pull-Down Stairs in Garage. Enclosed Florida Room under Heat and Air. New doors bathroom and Rooms. New microwave new ceramic tile  like wood in rooms, fresh paint inside and outside new backslash in the kitchen fresh paint.
